name: 💙💛Frida Punk 066 - Frida Colours💛💙
description:
Milestone 66th Edition 🍾 

Frida had much to say. Particularly on the subject of colours she says: 
"Yellow -  madness and mystery
all the ghosts wear
clothes of this color, or at
least their underclothes, sickness fear
part of the sun and of happiness.

Dark blue — color of bad advertisements
and of good business" - Frida Kahlo
